A high-level probe in Nepal holds former prime minister K.P. Sharma Oli and other senior government officials .css-jfmysa{display:inline;word-break:break-word;} .css-1ankfgb{cursor:pointer;display:inline;word-break:break-word;} responsible for criminal negligence over the shootings in last year’s deadly youth uprising that killed 76 people, as the leak of the crucial report to a local publication has triggered criticisms due to its sensitive nature.

.css-12olg5w{max-inline-size:100vw;}

.css-1dxvmvv{display:-webkit-box;display:-webkit-flex;display:-ms-flexbox;display:flex;-webkit-box-pack:center;-ms-flex-pack:center;-webkit-justify-content:center;justify-content:center;max-inline-size:100vw;}

